2011-08-19T15:14:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/ftse-100-benchmark-stocks-resume-fall-in-london-on-concern-about-economy.html
U.K. stocks resumed their retreat,
sending the FTSE 100 Index down 0.6 percent to 5,060.31 at 4:13
p.m. in  London . The gauge briefly erased its losses after
earlier tumbling as much as 3.2 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
